GoverningSphereSpec.Label: ABANDONED BY THE WATER'S SIDE
GoverningSphereSpec.Description: If you don't have anywhere to put a physical object, it might end up here.

GoverningSphereSpec.Label: Front Steps
GoverningSphereSpec.Description: I need a mutual acquaintance to introduce me to Reverend Timothy - perhaps someone who shares his interests in theology or poetry.

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: The Rectory [Locked]
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description:
Reverend Timothy is a hospitable soul, but Terrence, his housekeeper, guards her employer fiercely. She doesn't want his innocent theological enthusiasms getting him in trouble with the New King's men.
 [You need an Introduction, or a mutual acquaintance marked with Lantern, Knock, or Sky -  perhaps someone who shares his interests in theology or poetry.]

GoverningSphereSpec.Label: A Smoky Room
GoverningSphereSpec.Description: I need a mutual acquaintance to introduce me to Denzil - someone in a similar trade, or someone who can appeal to his secret passion for saffron cake.

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: The Smithy [Locked]
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description:
Denzil Smith has more work than he needs, and he rarely opens his door to strangers.
[You need an Introduction, or a mutual acquaintance marked with Edge, Forge, or Heart - someone in a similar trade, or someone who can appeal to his secret passion for saffron cake.]

GoverningSphereSpec.Label: The Front Room
GoverningSphereSpec.Description: I need a mutual acquaintance to introduce me to the Killes - someone of stature, or someone who shares their interests.

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: Mrs and Mr Kille [Locked]
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: Mrs Kille the midwife is tall and gloomy. Mr Kille the undertaker is slight and wry. In these troubled times, both are wary of strangers. [You need a suitably marked Introduction; check the slot.]

GoverningSphereSpec.Label: Post Office Counter
GoverningSphereSpec.Description: A place of power, a place of knowledge, beneath the sheltering hand of his Majesty the King.

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: The Post Office [Locked]
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: The postmistress may have something for me - once I know what to ask for.

GoverningSphereSpec.Label: A Sea of Hostile Faces
GoverningSphereSpec.Description: Diplomacy? Or bribery?

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: The Sweet Bones [Locked]
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: After the Restoration of 1930, the New King's agents came looking for his enemies in these parts... and they weren't gentle about it. Since those days, the locals are suspicious of foreigners. No-one in the Sweet Bones will talk to me.
